dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Keith King. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Debra. How can I assist you today?
I need to file a new claim after an incident.
Of course, Debra. Can you provide me with the date of the incident and a brief description of what happened?
The incident occurred on the twenty second of July. My vehicle was rear-ended while parked.
Thank you, Debra. I'll note down the details. Can you also confirm the make and model of your vehicle?
It's a two zero one eight Toyota Camry.
Thank you for the information, Debra. We will process your claim accordingly. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you, Keith.
You're welcome, Debra. Thank you for choosing Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
